% Alphabetical Sorting Examples (APA 9.44-9.52)
% APA 7th Edition Chapter 9 - Reference List Ordering
% ================================================
% 
% This file contains examples for alphabetical sorting and ordering:
% - Name sorting with prefixes (de, von, etc.)
